subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Nick Calathes’s triple-double — 11 points, 13 rebounds and 11 assists — led Florida to an 82-54 victory over Creighton in Gainesville, moving the Gators into next week’s quarterfinals of the National Invitation Tournament.Florida (23-11), the defending two-time national champions, used a 14-0 spurt midway through the first half to take a 29-12 lead on its way to a 39-19 halftime advantage.
